      <title>尼日利亚蒂努布将税收和电力列为 2024 年优先事项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-01/nigeria-s-tinubu-lists-tax-and-electricity-as-2024-priorities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚总统博拉·蒂努布在新年致辞中表示，尼日利亚今年将简化税法并改善电力供应，以确保企业具有竞争力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-01/nigeria-s-tinubu-lists-tax-and-electricity-as-2024-priorities</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 06:25:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平对拜登表示中美应努力和平共处</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-01/china-us-should-strive-towards-peaceful-coexistence-xi-says-to-biden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平1月1日致信拜登，历史证明，坚持相互尊重、和平共处是中美两国深度修复的正确相处之道。关系紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-01/china-us-should-strive-towards-peaceful-coexistence-xi-says-to-biden</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 04:30:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾总统敦促中国在选举前维持和平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-01/taiwan-president-tsai-ing-wen-urges-china-to-keep-peace-in-new-year-s-day-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾总统蔡英文在新年致辞中呼吁北京帮助维护该地区的和平。两周前，台湾将举行一场竞争激烈的选举，这场选举的主要内容是围绕台湾与中国关系的辩论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-01/taiwan-president-tsai-ing-wen-urges-china-to-keep-peace-in-new-year-s-day-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 01:57:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>博里克表示智利已准备好在投资和就业方面实现经济复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-01/president-gabriel-boric-says-chile-s-economy-is-poised-for-comeback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利总统加布里埃尔·博里奇表示，由于经济已经稳定，明年该国国内生产总值将强劲增长，为更多投资和就业奠定基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-01/president-gabriel-boric-says-chile-s-economy-is-poised-for-comeback</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 2024 00:19:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前德克萨斯州美国众议员埃迪·伯尼斯·约翰逊去世，享年 88 岁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-31/influential-former-texas-us-rep-eddie-bernice-johnson-dies-at-88</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德克萨斯州达拉斯（美联社）——长期担任美国众议员的先驱埃迪·伯尼斯·约翰逊(Eddie Bernice Johnson)是一名来自得克萨斯州的护士，他作为该地区最有影响力的民主党人，为达拉斯地区带来了数亿联邦资金，他于周日去世。她88岁了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-31/influential-former-texas-us-rep-eddie-bernice-johnson-dies-at-88</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 23:04:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平誓言在“艰难”的一年后加强经济复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-31/xi-pledges-to-strengthen-economic-recovery-after-tough-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平承诺加强经济增长势头和创造就业机会，承认一些企业和公民经历了艰难的2023年，罕见地承认了中国面临的国内阻力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-31/xi-pledges-to-strengthen-economic-recovery-after-tough-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 12:54:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列周日袭击加沙中部至少 35 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-31/israeli-strikes-in-central-gaza-kill-at-least-35-as-netanyahu-says-war-will-continue-for-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加沙地带代尔巴拉赫（美联社）医院官员称，周日，以色列对加沙中部的袭击造成至少 35 人死亡，一天前，以色列总理拒绝国际社会要求停火的呼吁，表示战争将持续“数月”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-31/israeli-strikes-in-central-gaza-kill-at-least-35-as-netanyahu-says-war-will-continue-for-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 12:33:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球各地庆祝除夕夜，但战争留下了阴影</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-31/australians-and-new-zealanders-preparing-to-be-among-first-nations-to-ring-in-2024-with-fireworks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新年在纽约时代广场数千人的欢呼声中到来，一颗闪闪发光的水晶球降临，为一些人带来了 2024 年的希望，尽管世界各地持续不断的冲突抑制了庆祝活动，并在全球范围内引发了安全担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-31/australians-and-new-zealanders-preparing-to-be-among-first-nations-to-ring-in-2024-with-fireworks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 06:19:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国海军击沉胡塞武装船只，马士基停止红海航运</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-31/us-shoots-down-anti-ship-missiles-launched-by-houthi-targeting-maersk-vessel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[AP穆勒-马士基公司的一艘船只遭到胡塞武装袭击，导致重要水道的紧张局势大幅升级，该公司暂停了通过红海的运输。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-31/us-shoots-down-anti-ship-missiles-launched-by-houthi-targeting-maersk-vessel</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 01:23:33 GMT</pubDate>
